snippet.title: Tait's Take
snippet.description:
Hey cool people, 

My name is Chris Tait and I'd like to welcome you to "Tait's Take!" I started Tait's Take on Instagram in 2018 where I would review movies on my story every Tuesday. Seeing as though stories only last 24 hours, instead of highlighting 52 movie reviews, I decided to take my talents to YouTube. 

Hopefully you all enjoy the videos enough to subscribe to the channel. Look for new videos every week, and feel free to send over any TV or movie requests that you want me to check out.

I am currently based in New York City and the link to my Instagram page is below. Enjoy the ride!

-Tait
